data.description: Huron Plan by LGI Homes. The Huron is a master piece blending both form and function. This home includes thoughtful features such as a walk-in pantry, covered patio, ceiling fans, stainless steel appliances and so much more. The master bedroom is enormous with double sinks, bay windows, corner garden tub, separate shower and a walk-in closet that's bigger than most bedrooms in other homes. Homeowners at Bauer Landing enjoy a wonderful park, pavilions, and walking trails. With close proximity to the Houston Premium Outlets and everything Northwest Houston has to offer, Bauer Landing is the perfect place to call home!
